  [Text] O masses of our lofty Yemeni people everywhere: The 
rotten clique is perpetrating its evil scheme against our people 
and their brave Armed Forces. This clique aims at destroying 
the homeland and wasting its resources. The separatist gang -- 
which is rebelling against constitutional legitimacy, led by the 
butcher, who is immersed in the blood of conspiracies against 
our people, the so-called 'Ali Salim al-Bid, and his clique -- 
is retaliating against Yemeni unity, your greatest achievement 
in the contemporary age. It is firing its missiles and shells 
on your historical and political capital, Sanaa, in order to 
annihilate its peaceful people. 
  It is not strange to see this gang, which killed and 
displaced thousands of Yemeni people in the black events of 
January 1986, seeking alliance with all devils and losing all 
sense of nationalism. 
  The sons of your brave Armed Forces are now waging the most 
honorable battle to purge the country of their filth. We will 
soon announce to you the crushing of the forces of apostasy, 
which reneged faith in God while raising the slogan of Communist 
ideology. 

