<H3> <TI>   Wrapup of Reports on Events in Yemen; Casualty Tolls Noted </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Wrapup of Reports on Events in Yemen; Casualty Tolls Noted </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Correspondent Updates Battles </H4>

<F P=102> JN0705162594 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1432 GMT 7 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0705162594 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Live dispatch" by 'Abd-al-Ghani Nasir al-Shamiri, radio </F>
and television correspondent in Mukayris] 
  [Text] Dear listeners: God's peace and blessings be upon 
you. I greet you from the valiant Mukayris district in the Abyan 
Governorate. Here is the true account of the progress of the 
purging of the strongholds of treason and separation. As for 
the 20th Brigade in Mukayris, the secessionist, rebellious 
traitors imagined that through this brigade and the 
extraordinary amounts of ammunition stored in it, they would be 
able to declare separation from this brigade. However, they 
were disappointed, for their evil plotting boomeranged against 
them. Our faithful, unionist forces managed on Thursday [5 May] 
at 1100 to seize the brigade, keeping its ammunition to defend 
the Yemen of unity of democracy, the Yemen of wellbeing and 
peace. As for the personnel of this brigade, some of them 
surrendered, while the others were captured. 
  The vanguards of the faithful, unionist forces are marching 
to pounce on the remnants of the [word indistinct] traitors and 
rebels, hammering the last nails in the coffin of separatists 
who rebelled against constitutional legitimacy and harbored evil 
and ill intentions against this beloved homeland. However, the 
unbelievers plotted and planned, and God too planned, and the 
best of planners is God. [koranic verse] 
  The vanguards of our valiant unionist and legitimate forces 
are removing the remaining dens of traitors, pounding their 
heads, which harbor secessionist illusions, and making them 
taste the bitter consequences of their evil intentions and acts. 
In al-Dayqah area this morning, the al-Wahadah Brigade forces 
under the command of Staff Colonel 'Abdallah Mansur engaged the 
rebellious secessionist forces of the 30th Brigade. Their 
forward forces were destroyed by our valiant, unionist forces, 
the defenders of unity, democracy, and constitutional 
legitimacy. Many personnel were detained and the entire 
equipment of those two brigades [as heard] were seized. 
  Our forces are now continuing to liquidate other units that 
continue to persist in their course of injustice, misguidance, 
rebellion, and separation. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

