<H4>    Scud Missile Hits Sanaa; Family Killed </H4>

<F P=102> NC1105092994 Paris AFP in English 0922 GMT 11 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1105092994 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Doha, May 11 (AFP) -- A Scud missile hit the Yemeni 
capital Sanaa on Wednesday [11 May] killing several people, a 
northern Yemeni spokesman said quoted by the QATARI NEWS AGENCY. 
  The missile, fired by southern forces, hit an industrial 
site 
in the centre of the city, and an entire family was among those 
killed, the agency said. 

</TEXT>

