<H3> <TI>   Russian Foreign Ministry Calls For Cease-Fire </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Foreign Ministry Calls For Cease-Fire </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA1005190694 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1500 GMT 10 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1005190694 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The leadership of federal Russia has called on the 
two sides fighting in Yemen to immediately halt all military 
operations. It said in a statement issued by the Foreign 
Ministry that whatever the differences between the disputing 
parties and whatever ends they had in mind could not constitute 
a justification for bloodshed and fratricidal strife or the 
suffering of the Yemeni people, nor justify the destruction of 
what is new. 

</TEXT>

