<H3> <TI>   Salih Confers With German Ambassador 7 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Salih Confers With German Ambassador 7 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0705152394 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1400 GMT 7 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0705152394 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, 
chairman of the Presidential Council, received in his office 
today the German ambassador to our country. They reviewed many 
fields of cooperation and issues of interest to both friendly 
countries, as well as the ongoing developments in our country. 
  During the meeting, the brother chairman lauded the level of 
bilateral cooperation and bilateral relations. He also voiced 
appreciation for the generous German aid to the development 
march in our country, and stressed our country's eagerness to 
enhance bilateral relations and expand the scope of cooperation 
in the interest of both friendly peoples. 

</TEXT>

