Middle East. Since when has America been keen about peace? 
America is the real enemy of peace. Since when has America been 
eager about the right or liberties of peoples? America is the 
real enemy of peoples, the real enemy of freedom. [passage 
omitted] 
  Against whom is America continuing to arm itself? Against 
Hungary, against Lithuania? Against which small state still 
