  [Text] Al-'Arish, Egypt, May 10 (MENA)--A group of 121 
Palestinian security men arrived at al-'Ajurah airport from 
[name indistinct] tonight aboard three Saudi aircraft. Other 
troops will arrive from Yemen later, said Palestinian security 
director Major General Nasr Yusuf. 
  Other Palestinian forces from Somalia and Libya will also 
arrive later, he said. 

