<H3> <TI>   Meets With Mubarak </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meets With Mubarak </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1105085394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0835 GMT 11 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1105085394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 11 May (MENA)--President Husni Mubarak 
received Yemeni Foreign Minister Muhammad Salim Basindwah at the 
Presidential Office this morning. The meeting was attended by 
Assistant Foreign Minister Badr Hammam. 
  The Yemeni foreign minister arrived in Cairo last night on a 
brief visit to Egypt to hand President Mubarak a message from 
Yemeni President 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih. 

</TEXT>

