<H3> <TI>   Saddam Receives Message From Jordan's King Husayn </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Saddam Receives Message From Jordan's King Husayn </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0805103094 Baghdad INA in Arabic 0920 GMT 8 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN0805103094 </F>
<F P=104>  Baghdad INA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Baghdad, 8 May (INA)--President Saddam Husayn has 
received a thank-you cable from his brother His Majesty King 
Husayn Bin-Talal of the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan in reply to 
a cable his excellency had sent to his majesty on the 
anniversary of his assumption of his Constitutional authorities. 
The cable says: 
  We received with appreciation your brotherly congratulations 
on the anniversary of our assumption of Constitutional 
authorities. As we send your excellency our sincere thanks, we 
beseech almighty God to preserve you and grant you success in 
serving your fraternal country. Please accept our heartfelt 
wishes of good health, happiness, and success. 

</TEXT>

