<H3> <TI>   No Further Transfer of Powers 11 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    No Further Transfer of Powers 11 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1105080594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0700 GMT 11 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1105080594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Senior Army sources state that the IDF [Israel 
Defense Forces] will not transfer any powers to the Palestinians 
in the Gaza Strip today. Yesterday about 140 Palestinian 
policemen entered an installation in Dayr al-Balah, where they 
remain for the time being. Today several dozen more policemen 
are slated to enter the Gaza Strip. Our correspondent Karmela 
Menashe reports that over the next few days more Palestinian 
policemen will prepare in the area for the transfer of power to 
their hands. 

</TEXT>

