  [Text] Some of the Golan Heights entrepreneurs and 
investors are preparing to continue running their businesses 
under Syrian sovereignty. Moreover, they say they have learned 
that this issue was anchored in the proposals Israel has 
submitted to Syria. 
  Investments amounting to hundreds of millions of shekels 
continue to be made in the Golan Heights industry, agriculture, 
and infrastructure. A major part of the investments come from 
government funds. 

</TEXT>

