unity. 
  BABIL concludes by saying: The unity which the Yemenis have 
built with their blood and sweat is invulnerable to 
fragmentation. That unity will remain the cure for the wounds of 
sabotage and treachery. 
  The paper stresses that unity and unionists will always 
triumph. 

