  [Text] Baghdad, May 7, INA -- AL-JUMHURIYAH daily has 
stressed that the current events and the killing in Yemen have 
been arranged by the United States of America and its satellites 
from the Arab reactionary countries. 
  In its editorial today, AL-JUMHURIYAH said that America 
wanted form the killing in Yemen to seize control the oil in the 
north and the south of the country at the same time and the 
