reactionary countries which move within the American orbit only. 
  The paper added that the current American plan in Yemen is 
to 
preserve the formal Yemeni unity to secure the control on all 
Yemeni oil. It went on to say that the regretted events in 
Yemen were no more than implementing a general American-Zionist 
plan. 
  The paper strongly denounced the double standered of the 
American stand towards the Yemeni unity. It also pointed out to 
the Saudi conspiracy against the Yemeni unity following Sanaa 
joining to the Arab Cooperation Council. 

