<H3> <TI>   'Arafat, Castro Hold Talks in Pretoria </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    'Arafat, Castro Hold Talks in Pretoria </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1105183694 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
