<F P=102>   TA1105171694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1505 GMT 11 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA1105171694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Hayim Hecht] </F>
  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Addressing the Knesset plenum 
today, Likud Chairman Binyamin Netanyahu announced: The day on 
which the agreement with the PLO was signed was a dark day. 
This document is a disaster, a historical mistake. 
  [Begin Netanyahu recording] Furtively, surreptitiously, 
perfidiously, they are trying to divert the public's attention 
from the signed-and-sealed next stage: Samaria and Judaea, the 
Jordan Rift Valley and the eastern slopes of the Judaea 
Mountains, as well as Jerusalem, whose turn to be united with 
the PLO will come during this obsequious government's course of 
action. 
  In Oslo, you envisioned the first stage of the Arab state 
from the sea to the desert. In Washington, you signed an 
agreement to love and cherish 'Arafat, the chairman of the 
murder syndicate. And in Cairo, publicly degraded and 
humiliated in a live broadcast aired to the entire world, you 
signed the document of surrender. [end recording] 
  Rabin stared tiredly at Netanyahu, then waved his hand 
dismissively and slowly uttered: Baloney. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

