<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Poll Views Chance of Peace With Palestinians </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0505123194 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 5 May 94 p 1 </F>
