<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Public opinion poll conducted by the Dahaf Institute under </F>
the management of Dr. Mina Tzemah] 
  [Text] Question: After the signing of the agreement on 
the implementation of autonomy in Gaza and Jericho first, what 
are the chances for the establishment of peace between Israel 
and the Palestinians? 

  -  very high -- 7 percent 
  -  high -- 28 percent 
  -  low -- 35 percent 
  -  none -- 27 percent 
  -  no reply -- 3 percent 

    The poll was conducted on 4 May and covered 566 interviewees 
who constitute a representative sample of the adult Israeli 
population. The maximum margin of error is 4 percent. 

