94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1205102994 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Prime Minister Rafiq al-Hariri left his house at 
1000 today. Earlier, he received Ministers Marwan Hamadah, 
'Abdallah al-Amin, and Jean 'Ubayd. He also received a 
delegation from Tripoli led by Misbah al-Ahdab, which conveyed 
its support for al-Hariri's political line and urged him to 
