<H3> <TI>   President Receives Yemen's Oil Minister 11 May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President Receives Yemen's Oil Minister 11 May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN1205073994 Manama WAKH in Arabic 0530 GMT 12 May 94 </F>
