  [Text] Al-Jarf, 11 May (WAKH) -- His Highness Shaykh Zayid 
Bin-Sultan Al Nuhayyan, president of the United Arab Emirates 
[UAE], this evening received Salih Abu-Bakr Bin-Husaynun, Yemeni 
